apps/783770/extras/a041e097ae520348f3b9a394611aa719.mp4?t=1754442298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Individual Skill</strong></u><br>Claim victory on the battlefield by constantly developing your skills amidst various variables and the gunfire of cutting edge weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783770/extras/5241e32b6e2e60e2df8c5d3e0b551963.poster.avif?t=1754442298\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783770/extras/5241e32b6e2e60e2df8c5d3e0b551963.webm?t=1754442298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783770/extras/5241e32b6e2e60e2df8c5d3e0b551963.mp4?t=1754442298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
